The course is built on collaboration of teachers from different units of the field. The teachers choose 6-7 works from world literature, one lecture and one seminar being dedicated to each text. In the lecture the teacher describes the background and contexts of the text, introduces the author and distributes tasks for the seminar.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Õpiväljundiks on tutvus maailmakirjanduse uuemate tekstidega ning oskus neid analüüsida.  The learning outcome is to get to know the newer texts of world literature and skills of analysing them.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The learning outcome is to get to know the newer texts of world literature and skills of analysing them.
